    • isCached

      public boolean isCached()
      Beschreibung aus Schnittstelle kopiert: Leveler
      Returns true if the leveler is currently cached.
      You should avoid using not cached levelers, specially when the player is online.
      Using uncached levelers can cause database conflicts. While the database is protected, only one data can be written to the database.
      Angegeben von:
